Pidgin Plugin to automatically reply when some 'buzzes' you by sending an attention.

-----------------------------------------------------------
Installation
-----------------------------------------------------------

Linux

To download the files run:
    git clone git@github.com:jcul/Pidgin-Buzz-Autoreply.git

Or download the files manually.

Type
    make
to compile the plugin (you will need the pidgin development headers)

To install to ~/.purple/plugins, type
    make install


Windows:

Download the dll from the downloads section to %APPDATA%\.purple\plugins


-----------------------------------------------------------
Usage
-----------------------------------------------------------

Enable and set the auto respond message via the plugins menu
